#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/3.2/guides/smallrye-graphql.adoc:957
msgid "the original request (Query/Mutation)"
msgstr "オリジナルのリクエスト(Query/Mutation)"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/3.2/guides/smallrye-graphql.adoc:958
